text:
Perfect timing.
I have something to discuss about the next outfit.

Thank you, Producer-san.
Uh, about the next outfit...?

Yeah, 283 Production is making matching
outfits for everyone, and they'll be arriving soon.

What kind of outfits will they be...?
...Hehe, I'm so looking forward to it.

Haha, that's good to hear.
I'm sure they'll be perfect for everyone.
...Outfits to wear with everyone from 283 Production...

...Will I be able to stand on stage with
everyone from 283 Production...?

Yeah, that's the plan.
I'm looking forward to what kind of stage it'll be!
